{"tid":1016083,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好做中學功課","createTime":"2019-02-10T14:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T13:26:14.000Z","uid":196828,"like":135,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e960ffc0def45c1aa8527a6b790107911b377dc4","tid":1016083,"uid":196828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"要考公開試自己操足三年卷其實更有效！<br />\n<br />\n垃圾教局指引要派功課，啲教畜自己唔想失業又唔為學生抗爭，結果咪浪費晒下一代啲青春係啲無謂嘅功課度囉！<br />\n<br />\n老實講，用咁多時間做啲成效不彰嘅功課，不如睇下大學有咩讀，再自己發掘一下有咩係對自己日後有幫助嘅仲好啦！想讀文學嘅睇文言，想讀IT 嘅學python, 想讀business 嘅玩下Bloomberg terminal &amp; VBA, 趁中學冇咁多誘惑同工作，自己睇書學下之後要投放大量時間嘅嘢對你個人發展更好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最多咪攞你老母乜叉小過大過見家長囉，大學收左教局錢只係睇公開試成績，唔L理你中學內部堆白癡紀錄，就算見校長都駁你唔倒啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新一年希望下一代可以唔駛再俾堆讀唔成書嘅教畜㩒住黎玩，咁就一世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cbd68c572be4468861af3e243c7239de5894f9","tid":1016083,"uid":192491,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"如果我中學就睇大學野..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4b62b43503385253982f709b84aa9b52dbb832","tid":1016083,"uid":35698,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"早幾年有呢個post咪好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2922747e23f1d659f4a1782dc133b04381cff111","tid":1016083,"uid":196828,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"25cbd68c572be4468861af3e243c7239de5894f9","tid":1016083,"uid":192491,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"如果我中學就睇大學野..<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"真心中學學VBA, 識寫三國體嘅人真心唔少，小隱隱於野，大隱隱於市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同學見倒呢個post 記得ignore the naysayers, no one